Given an array of integers A sorted in non-decreasing order, 
return an array of the squares of each number, also in sorted non-decreasing order.

class Solution {
    public int[] sortedSquares(int[] A) {
        int i;
        for(i = 0;i < A.length; i++)
        {
            A[i] = A[i] * A[i];
        }
        Arrays.sort(A);
        return A;
    }
}
